{"success": true, "message": "Fetched question.", "data": {"showTimer": true, "showAttemptInsight": true, "playSounds": true, "dontShowCorrectAnswerImmediately": false, "_id": "648b5a64417cc3fb48d65fa2", "type": "singleCorrect", "level": 3, "category": null, "approximateTimeRequired": 180, "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText": null, "source": "EM", "classes": [], "exams": ["615d76b2c52ffa3c944600df"], "subjects": ["615d708dbd4a37c4058ee5a8"], "chapters": ["615d6fed2b295b085ab6eba2"], "topics": [], "concepts": [], "microConcepts": [], "questionLabels": [], "previousYearPapers": [{"_id": "615d92ebde3d91842a5cf7dd", "title": "JEE Main 2015 (11 Apr Online)", "isVisible": true}], "question": {"text": "A thin convex lens of focal length <math><mi>f</mi></math>&nbsp;is put on a plane mirror as shown in the figure. When an object is kept at a distance <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi></math>&nbsp;from the lens-mirror combination, its image is formed at a distance <math><mfrac><mrow><mi>a</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>3</mn></mrow></mfrac></math> in front of the combination. The value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>a</mi></math>&nbsp;is:<br /><img src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq/jee_main/beb6545b-56d2-48cc-a8c8-5fb1f2d2fbeb-image.png\" style=\"width: 150px; height: 136px;\" />", "image": null}, "options": [{"id": "EY48H", "text": "<math><mn>2</mn><mi>f</mi></math>", "image": null, "isCorrect": true}, {"id": "rKvXr", "text": "<math><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac><mi>f</mi></math>", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "ObEEv", "text": "<math><mn>3</mn><mi>f</mi></math>", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "qMmov", "text": "<math><mi>f</mi></math>", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "<img src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq/jee_main/f6e1dfc5-7fe1-451c-8ca5-d7902bdec18f-image.png\" style=\"width: 140px; height: 138px;\" /><br />Equivalent power of combination is<br /><br /><math><msub><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>e</mi><mi>f</mi><mi>f</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><msub><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>l</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>s</mi></mrow></msub><mo>+</mo><msub><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>r</mi></mrow></msub></math> ...(i)<br /><br /><math><mo>&#8757;</mo><msub><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>&#160;</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></math> for plane mirror and <math><msub><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>l</mi><mi>e</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>s</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>f</mi></mrow></mfrac></math><br /><br />Also combination behaves as a mirror. So. <math><msub><mrow><mi>P</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>e</mi><mi>f</mi><mi>f</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>f</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>r</mi></mrow></msub></mrow></mfrac></math><br /><br />In equation (i)<br /><br /><math><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>f</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>&#160;</mi></mrow></msub></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>f</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>&#8658;</mo><msub><mrow><mi>f</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>r</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>f</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac></math><br /><br />By mirror formula<br /><br /><math><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><msub><mrow><mi>f</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>&#160;</mi></mrow></msub></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>u</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>v</mi></mrow></mfrac></math><br /><br />Here <math><mi>u</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>&#160;</mi><mo>-</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>,</mo><mi>&#160;</mi><mi>v</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>a</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>3</mn></mrow></mfrac><mo>,</mo><mi>&#160;</mi><msub><mrow><mi>f</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>m</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>r</mi><mi>o</mi><mi>r</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mi>&#160;</mi><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>f</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac></math><br /><br /><math><mo>&#8658;</mo><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>f</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><mrow><mo>-</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn></mrow><mrow><mo>-</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>a</mi></mrow></mfrac></math><br /><br /><math><mo>&#8658;</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>f</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>4</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>a</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>&#8658;</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>f</mi></math>", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "masterId": "MOGJMPYQ26795589", "numericalLowerLimit": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "bucket": "", "isRemoved": false, "cpyqbSubjects": ["61bb58181213731910ea0b70", "61c055eae8ce0dc8a5c62d33", "616057750283de43c87e3e1b", "61964fe0a5a5260118868021", "61964f81a5a526011886801d", "629f39e4ac11b26562e0625b", "616057920283de43c87e3e1e", "615f0c729476412f48314dab", "61a8a2c2e8ce0dc8a5c62d2d", "629105adee9e3ae00d63352b", "629f385f263330a77be9fa7d", "616056cd0283de43c87e3e15", "616057190283de43c87e3e18", "62962075e7f8e9ac4daeafd7", "64d50bd73df7f4a7f3017f6f", "66b79b34d4b564dfab4f94cc", "678ea9a09cc79e5f592bdc11", "67fa5fef4468eb1307ceb0ad", "6807d2ad647479b8e8696479"], "cpyqbChapters": ["61964c922db938c3ec5c87e8", "6160243a86b518ff2afd9379", "6160243ae896b71d7f0f03d9", "61bb820fc1f688a120dfda9f", "61964c9102fe1de035852896", "61e7bd71a2dd607688d6c01b", "61c08989e3eba41a9e71354b", "61602437a04b762ba7dfcb47", "61602438690b07c861db4cc9", "6160243b738